# 📊 Netflix Data Analysis Project

## 🔍 Overview
Analyzed Netflix dataset using Excel and Google Sheets to uncover content trends and insights.

## 📈 Key Insights
- Movies dominate Netflix content (~70%)
- Rapid growth in content after 2015
- Top genres include Drama, Documentaries, and Stand-up Comedy

## 🛠 Tools & Techniques
- Excel & Google Sheets
- Data Cleaning
- Pivot Tables
- Data Visualization (Bar, Pie, Line Charts)

